attributes.review: this app has no design features that are in any way attractive to the eye. when i took a look at it, my eyes started to bleed out. in the end, my face was all red, and my hair ended up becoming dyed permanently. my face will forever be scarred, looking like this:🩸👄🩸this app took me about 16 years to download, but as soon as i entered the app, it said i “couldn’t download because i’m underaged”. so now i will have to wait another 16 years to vote for my dear beloved president 😻😻😻😻 i am also ashamed to see that it is entitled “trump 2020”, when in fact, donald j trump was not born in 2020 🤬 i am outraged to say the least. when opening the app, i almost passed out due to the tiny spinning “T” ok the opening screen. it went way too fast for my bleeding eyes, and i almost couldn’t bear it. in the end, the pain is still not as horrible as the design of this app. terrible job 🥰✨👏👏
